# Book Endpoints

### Create Book
POST http://localhost:8000/books/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Test Book",
  "author": "John Doe",
  "description": "A test book",
  "file": "@./test.txt"
}

### List Books
GET http://localhost:8000/books/?page=1

### Get Book Analysis
GET http://localhost:8000/books/1/analysis

### Recommendations
GET http://localhost:8000/recommendations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
